<div class="section-container mt-16 mb-16">
    <div class="glass-panel" style="padding: 3rem;">
        <h1 class="aura-title mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-dim mb-8"><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

        <div class="legal-content">
            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">1. Data We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-dim mb-8">Nomad Budgeter is a client-side calculator. We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or transmit your financial inputs (income, expenses, city selections) to any server. All calculations run entirely in your browser.</p>

            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">2. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-dim mb-8">We use only <strong>essential cookies</strong> to remember your cookie consent preference. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or any third-party analytics that identify you personally.</p>

            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">3. Global Privacy Control (GPC)</h2>
            <p class="text-dim mb-8">We respect your browser's <strong>Global Privacy Control</strong> signal. If GPC is enabled, we treat it as a legally binding opt-out of any data sale or sharing, in compliance with CCPA, GDPR, and the Colorado Privacy Act.</p>

            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">4. Third-Party APIs</h2>
            <p class="text-dim mb-4">Our calculator queries two external APIs to provide live data:</p>
            <ul class="mb-8" style="padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-dim);">
                <li class="mb-2"><strong>ExchangeRate-API</strong> — for currency conversion rates</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><strong>API-Ninjas</strong> — for city population and income tax data</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-dim mb-8">These requests are made from your browser directly. We do not proxy or log these requests.</p>

            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">5. Affiliate Links</h2>
            <p class="text-dim mb-8">This site contains affiliate links to partner services (e.g., SafetyWing, Wise, Lexidy). Clicking these links may set cookies on the partner's domain. We receive a commission if you purchase through these links, at no additional cost to you.</p>

            <h2 class="mb-4" style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem;">6. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-dim">For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="text-aura-primary">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
